- Bindings: 11 (cells, survivors, cell, neighborCount, adjacentDeadCells, x, y, dx, dy, nx, ny, isLive, alreadyAdded, born) = 14
- Invocations: 7 (filter, countNeighbors, filter, countNeighbors, containsCell, containsCell, push, spread x2) = 14... let me count carefully
