  - adjacentDeadCells.push = 1
  - adjacentDeadCells.filter = 1
  - countNeighbors (in born filter) = 1
  Total: 7 invocations = 14
- Conditionals: 3 (neighborCount===2||3 is 1, if dx===0&&dy===0 is 1, if !isLive&&!alreadyAdded is 1) = 12
- Loops: 3 (for cells, for dx, for dy) = 15
- Assignments: 5 (survivors=, adjacentDeadCells=[], nx=, ny=, isLive=, alreadyAdded=, born=) = 7 assignments = 42

